## State Ownership Summary

| **Data** | **Where** | **Why** |
|----------|-----------|--------|
| Dark mode toggle | `SiteLayoutCard` component `@tracked` | UI state, not content |
| Navigation links | `SiteLayoutCard.navLinks` | Shared across all pages |
| Section order | `SiteLayoutCard.sections` | Page composition |
| Section content | Individual section card instances | Independently editable |
| Feature tiles | `containsMany(FeatureTileField)` in section | Compound data |
| Catalog items | `containsMany(CatalogItemField)` in section | Compound data |
| Theme colors | `ThemeCard` linked via `cardInfo.theme` | Shared styling |
| Animation state | Component modifiers | Transient UI |

